      "writtenOn": "2015-12-04T17:30:34Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "If you check out add_finger_event(), you\u0027ll see that the last number is just some arbitrary \"state\" number. Previously, it was simply being used to indicate a \"touch down\" (state \u003d 1) or \"touch up\" (state \u003d 0).\n\nI\u0027m just taking advantage of the extra bits to indicate which finger (1st or 2nd) is being used. I\u0027ve updated this function to make that more obvious and added a comment.",
